commit.message: Adding some explanatory text to the parameters in the UI
Making the generator more modular so it can be reused in the bot
Added option to increase number of user tweets fetched
Adding duplicate buttons at bottom of fusion screen so you don't have to scroll back up
Adding ability to specify N and M
Switching to Pug for HTML rendering
Now completely functional, just needs a lot of prettying up
I'm an idiot who commits node modules
